name: Empress
description: R.p.Callahan is a traditional and digital artist based out of the USA. Self taught in illustration and painting he won many art awards throughout school and has done commissions for the United States Air Force, Craig Alanson Ex Force series, 3D models for James Alutcher, and many book and album covers. Recently he was accepted into Las Cruces Space Pop Art Festival to celebrate opening of Space Port USA.
